episodes.title: This Is TERRIFYING - The Aussie Cult Murders
episodes.description:
In this episode, we break down the shocking case of Brendan Luke Stevens and the Australian religious group known as The Saints — a fringe faith community at the centre of one of the most disturbing cult-linked deaths in recent memory.

In January 2022, eight-year-old Elizabeth Rose Struhs died at her home in Toowoomba, Queensland, Australia, after members of a sect called The Saints deliberately withheld her prescribed insulin for six days while she suffered from type 1 diabetes.
